OL,7,FMore than 1,600 fines were issued to
OL,8,Fdrivers in just over a year for
OL,9,Fentering a Derby bus lane ` with
OL,10,Fresidents on the street also being
OL,11,Fcaught out by cameras.
OL,13,Fis closed to traffic between 7am and
OL,14,F9am Monday to Friday, except for
OL,15,Fcyclists and buses.
OL,17,FAnyone breaching the restriction risks
OL,18,Fa #70 fine as cameras are fixed around
OL,19,Fthe street.
