OL,5,CDerby
OL,7,FIt states that between January 5,
OL,8,F2023, and February 8, 2024 a total of
OL,9,F1,665 fines were issued to motorists
OL,10,Fbreaching the no entry restriction
OL,11,Fbetween 7am and 9am.
OL,13,FThe 1,600-plus fines within that
OL,14,Ftimeframe have seen the council net
OL,15,Fmore than #55,000 in income.
OL,17,FThe council said 64 fines had been
OL,18,Frescinded, but no further information
OL,19,Fwas given as to why.
