OL,7,FDerby City Council says the bus lane
OL,8,Frestriction at Church Lane will remain
OL,9,Fin place as it has "successfully"
OL,10,Freduced traffic in the area at peak
OL,11,Fmorning times.
OL,13,FResidents living on Church Lane say
OL,14,Fthe measures have improved the road as
OL,15,Fthere were previous concerns it was
OL,16,Fbeing used as a "rat run" by drivers
OL,17,Fwanting to beat congested traffic on
OL,18,Fthe A6 Duffield Road.
