OL,7,FIan Plackett, who has lived on the
OL,8,Fstreet for 13 years, said: "I'm
OL,9,Fusually anti this kind of thing. I am
OL,10,Fterrified of driving in Nottingham
OL,11,Fbecause there are cameras everywhere.
OL,13,F"But in this case, I think it has been
OL,14,Fa great positive and calmed down the
OL,15,Frat run.
OL,17,F"I think others may see it as
OL,18,Firritating as they may have to go the
OL,19,Flong way around to get to the schools,
OL,20,Fbut overall I think it has been a good
OL,21,Fthing.
