OL,7,FA spokesperson for Derby City Council
OL,8,Fsaid: "The restriction evolved from
OL,9,FCovid-19 emergency measures to provide
OL,10,Froom through the village for social
OL,11,Fdistancing, mainly for those walking
OL,12,Fto the two primary schools in the area.
OL,14,F"Following a widespread consultation
OL,15,Fexercise with residents, there was
OL,16,Foverwhelming support for the
OL,17,Frestriction to remain.
OL,19,F"The signing is correct to national
OL,20,Fguidance and reflects the current
OL,21,FTraffic Regulation Order.
